{"tid":1953444,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"新巴城巴25.6米巴士登場！","createTime":"2020-04-01T07:43:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-06T12:12:15.000Z","uid":164435,"like":12,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"d0051711f1e2226fc3b0104c5337f1b55af78e0c","tid":1953444,"uid":164435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T07:43:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/NWFBCitybus/posts/672553336825969\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FNWFBCitybus%2Fposts%2F672553336825969&d=fPi9TpucIiEDTgLGk%2FOmnQfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=1c0779ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/NWFBCitybus/posts/672553336825969</a><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iqnte3Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fiqnte3Y.jpg&h=f5d42419&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n【25.6米三層巴士登場！】<br />\n<br />\n我哋正式宣佈，兩部25.6米三層巴士即將投入服務！相信會成為全球最有特色嘅巴士👑。呢兩部巴士擁有4個輪椅位♿️，座位方面係原來12.8米巴士嘅3倍，除此之外，巴士亦有3道門、2條樓梯及1部升降機，方便乘客上落。<br />\n<br />\n兩部新巴士都將會喺新巴城巴嘅繁忙路線試行！而我哋嘅車長都加緊訓練，務求可以駕駛呢部超級陸上巨無霸征服港島嘅橫街窄巷！有咗呢兩部特大巴士，大家以後搭長途車就唔怕無位坐啦！<br />\n<br />\n#新巴 #城巴 #NWFB #Citybus #25點6米巴士 #4月1日特別消息 #多軸轉向 <span style=\"color: red;\">#愚人節快樂 #Aprilfool</span><br />\n<br />\nFrom新巴城巴Facebook <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/NWFBCitybus/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FNWFBCitybus%2F&d=fPi9TpucIiEDTgLGk%2FOmnQfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=ce92a4c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/NWFBCitybus/</a>"},{"pid":"ad36e87f93403e8577e4bcf8b0536bb313c4f53b","tid":1953444,"uid":239571,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T07:45:21.000Z","msg":"咪玩啦 都放唔落我條長腿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6cef7209e13211ff51509c25d17eda513d0bd12","tid":1953444,"uid":191926,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T07:46